[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Task Content[39m                                                                                                                                            [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Task B: Auto-create pipeline run on direct dispatch[39m                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m**Parent design:** cb-7aa91d[39m                                                                                                                               [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m**Wave:** 1[39m                                                                                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m**Repo:** cobuild[39m                                                                                                                                          [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Scope[39m                                                                                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mMake `cobuild dispatch <id>` work without requiring a prior `cobuild init`. Auto-create a pipeline_run on the fly if one does not exist. This fixes gate [39m  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mcommands (`cobuild investigate`, `cobuild review`, etc.) failing for directly-dispatched work items.[39m                                                       [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Changes[39m                                                                                                                                                 [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m1. `internal/cmd/dispatch.go` — after loading the work item, before building the prompt:[39m                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   - Call `cbStore.GetRun(ctx, task.ID)`[39m                                                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   - If no run exists, create one via `cbStore.CreateRunWithMode`:[39m                                                                                         [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     - `design_id = task.ID`[39m                                                                                                                               [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     - `project = projectName`[39m                                                                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     - `workflow = inferWorkflowFromType(task.Type)` — bug → bug, design → design, task → task[39m                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     - `current_phase = firstPhaseOf(workflow)` from pipeline config[39m                                                                                       [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     - `status = "active"`[39m                                                                                                                                 [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m     - `mode = "manual"`[39m                                                                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m   - Print a one-line notice: `Auto-created pipeline run for <id> (workflow: <wf>, phase: <phase>)`[39m                                                        [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m2. Add helper `inferWorkflowFromType(wiType string) string` in `internal/cmd/dispatch.go` or `internal/config/config.go`[39m                                   [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m3. Add helper `firstPhaseOf(workflow string, cfg *Config) string` that looks up the first phase of a workflow from the loaded config, with a sensible [39m     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mfallback[39m                                                                                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Acceptance criteria[39m                                                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] `cobuild dispatch <id>` succeeds when no pipeline run exists (creates one)[39m                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] A one-line notice is printed when auto-creation happens[39m                                                                                              [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] The auto-created run has the correct workflow, first phase, and mode=manual[39m                                                                          [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] `cobuild investigate <bug-id>` succeeds after `cobuild dispatch <bug-id>` (no more "no pipeline run" errors)[39m                                         [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] `cobuild init` still works as before and is idempotent with the auto-create path (running init after auto-create should detect the existing run and [39m [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mnot duplicate)[39m                                                                                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] `go build ./...` and `go vet ./...` pass[39m                                                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] Integration check: dispatch a bug directly, then run a gate command — confirm it works end-to-end[39m                                                    [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Out of scope[39m                                                                                                                                            [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Changing the set of phases or workflows (handled by Task C/D)[39m                                                                                            [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Deprecating `cobuild init` — it still has value for explicit workflow selection and batch setup[39m                                                          [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Design Context (from cb-7aa91d)[39m                                                                                                                         [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m**Dispatch reliability: Stop hook, fix-phase for bugs, auto pipeline runs**[39m                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m## Problem[39m                                                                                                                                                 [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mDispatched agents are failing to complete their work reliably. Of 4 recent dispatches (pf-70df40, pf-326239, pf-09df7a, pf-21779f), none ran `cobuild [39m     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mcomple[39m                                                                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m… +475 lines …[39m                                                                                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231miptions | Update to reflect new default |[39m                                                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m| `cobuild explain` output | Pipeline explanation | Already reads from config/skills, but verify it renders the new workflows correctly and mentions the [39m  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mescalation |[39m                                                                                                                                               [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m### Discoverability checks for the orchestrator agent (M)[39m                                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mThe orchestrator agent (the one calling `cobuild dispatch`) is the most likely caller to need this. Before creating a bug work item, M should:[39m             [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m1. Read the bug symptoms from the user[39m                                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m2. Mentally run through the 7 escalation criteria[39m                                                                                                          [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m3. If any apply, add `--label needs-investigation` when creating the work item[39m                                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m4. If creating via skill, the skill should prompt M to make this decision explicitly[39m                                                                       [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mThis belongs in the CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md that the orchestrator reads, in the "creating work items" section. It should be a small decision tree, not [39m      [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mburied prose.[39m                                                                                                                                              [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m### Fail-loud signal[39m                                                                                                                                       [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mIf dispatch ever routes a bug to the `fix` phase and the fix agent realises mid-session that the cause is genuinely unknown or the blast radius is [39m        [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231munclear, it should:[39m                                                                                                                                        [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m1. Stop implementing[39m                                                                                                                                       [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m2. Append findings so far to the bug[39m                                                                                                                       [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m3. Add the `needs-investigation` label[39m                                                                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m4. Exit and let the orchestrator re-dispatch through the investigation flow[39m                                                                                [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mThis self-escalation path prevents agents from flailing on bugs they can't fix safely.[39m                                                                     [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m### New Task for Wave 3[39m                                                                                                                                    [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m**Task I: Escalation documentation and self-escalation**[39m                                                                                                   [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Update all docs/skills listed in the table above[39m                                                                                                         [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Add escalation criteria to `skills/fix/fix-bug.md` with inline decision checklist[39m                                                                        [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Add bug-creation guidance to CLAUDE.md / generated AGENTS.md: "when creating a bug, apply these criteria to decide labeling"[39m                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Add self-escalation protocol to `skills/fix/fix-bug.md`[39m                                                                                                  [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- Verify `cobuild explain` renders the new workflows cleanly[39m                                                                                               [49m
[48;5;237m                                                                                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231mDependencies: blocked by Task C (needs `skills/fix/fix-bug.md` to exist first)[39m                                                                             [49m
